  The Linux Thai HOWTO
  Poonlap Veeratanabutr, poon-v@fedu.uec.ac.jp
  v0.4, 4 August 1998

  This document describes how to use Thai language with Linux. This will
  cover setting Thai fonts, Thai keyboard and some Thai applications.
